Package: MRCIP
Type: Package
Title: MRCIP: A robust Mendelian randomization method accounting for correlated and idiosyncratic pleiotropy
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Siqi Xu
Maintainer: Siqi Xu <sqxu@hku.hk>
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Description:The package provides a Mendelian randomization approach for the inference of causal relationship between traits based on summary-level GWAS data, which accounts for the correlated pleiotropy and idiosyncratic pleiotropy. 
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
